A flange fitting (206) with a leak detection feature for an inner fluid conduit (202) and an outer fluid conduit (204) surrounding the inner fluid conduit, the flange fitting comprising:
a flange body having an inner portion (218) around an opening (214) of the inner fluid conduit, and
having an outer portion (220) around an opening (216) of the outer fluid conduit, the flange body having a sealing face surface (222) configured to mate with a cooperating flange fitting;
an inner leak detection passageway (234) formed in the inner portion (218) of the flange body, the inner leak detection passageway terminating at the sealing face surface (222);
an inner leak detection port (230) formed in the inner portion of the flange body, the inner leak detection port in fluid communication with the inner leak detection passageway (234), and the inner leak detection port being configured for fluid communication with a leak sensing apparatus;
and an outer leak detection passageway (226) formed in the outer portion (220) of the flange body, the outer leak detection passageway terminating at the sealing face surface (222); and
an outer leak detection port (238) formed in the outer portion of the flange body, the outer leak detection port in fluid communication with the outer leak detection passageway (226), and the outer leak detection port being configured for fluid communication with the leak sensing apparatus.

The flange fitting of claim 1, further comprising:
a first leakage collection conduit (210, 304) coupled to the inner leak detection port (230);
a first leak detector (308) coupled to the first leakage collection conduit (210, 304), the first leak detector being configured to sense fluid leakage into the inner leak detection passageway;
a second leakage collection conduit (212, 306) coupled to the outer leak detection port (238);
and
a second leak detector (310) coupled to the second leakage collection conduit (212, 306), the second leak detector being configured to sense fluid leakage into the outer leak detection passageway.

